{"tid":883742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實諾貝爾獎真係咁重要？","createTime":"2018-10-31T05:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T05:37:55.000Z","uid":389,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f786f2c038809756990d807a71ae9aa8c9e4e6","tid":883742,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"一個文學大師辭世，佢既所謂書迷竟然係咁感歎佢無諾貝爾文學獎。但堂堂一代宗師，連諾貝爾獎得主都要拜倒佢筆下，竟然要仰仗呢啲低級過自己成就既虛榮？<br />\n<br />\n金庸作品立足華文界，根本不而仰仗瑞典啲小圈子獎。而當羅素都拎到諾貝爾文學獎，其實金庸可以用書中中醫知識拎醫學獎，書中武功拎物理學獎架"},{"pid":"00f36d7e54a86bec00e2c2ea0c3c1e64e05d122d","tid":883742,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曲到圓</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但你打錯字,你輸左(不而仰仗)"},{"pid":"2c8b6b8cafb03ed1c7152a99d9e783258bdf7ce6","tid":883742,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"根本唔需要個獎去證明佢嘅貢獻 <br />\n多尻餘"},{"pid":"8e55501422e1e1ed6172c557e4a39d8b3fc1afe1","tid":883742,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f36d7e54a86bec00e2c2ea0c3c1e64e05d122d","tid":883742,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曲到圓</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但你打錯字,你輸左(不而仰仗)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"Ok you win滿意未"}]}